===Etymology===
Compare {{m|bo|འཛུགས||to insert; to plant}} ({{zh-ref|Sagart, 2017d}}; {{zh-ref|Hill, 2019}}), which STEDT (under PTB *m-(d)z(y)u(ː)k) derives from {{cog|sit-pro|*tsəwk||to pierce; to plant}}.

{{zh-ref|Sagart (2017)}} also compares it to {{cog|kac|achyo||to stab}}.

